description:
A convenient storage solution for your Outland Firecube Fire Pit. Webbing handles provide carrying options, and the zippered top contains any dust or debris that may come off the fire pit.

  • Made of durable 600-denier polyester with a polyurethane lining
  • Zippered top is easy to load
  • Pocket under of lid stores a lighter and other small items
name: Outland Living Firecube Carry Bag
